Project Title: High-Performance Image Cryptography via CUDA.Description:
A GPU-based application that utilizes massively parallel threads to perform bitwise XOR encryption on high-resolution images.GPU 
Usage: Explains how the encryptKernel handles one pixel per thread, achieving $O(1)$ complexity per pixel in parallel.
Build Instructions:Run make buildRun ./gpu_encryptor.exe
Proof of Execution: Paste the terminal output showing the encrypted hex values vs. the decrypted integers.
